Example:
<<<<<
1

hand effect:
[]
atta op 15
disc sl

hand effect:
[rd]
atta ow 3

hand effect:
[bl]
atta ow 3
>>>>>
This card should be used immediately, when it is drawn.

Example:
<<<<<
18

hand effect:
[]
invo sl
call rd
call gr
call bl

field effect:
[rd gr bl]
atta sl 17

field effect:
[]
atta op 26
>>>>>
If this card is invoked without interrupting the sequence, it will end up with 1 health.
Being in the field with 1HP should be worse than bing in the hand. 